{"lemma":"بِضْعَة","slug":"بِضْعَة","root":"ب.ض.ع","root_slug":"ب-ض-ع","root_link":"/words/roots/ب-ض-ع","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":true,"lemma_key":"بِضْع","root":"بضع","pos":"N","occurrence_count":2},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":1,"pos_tags":["noun"],"has_etymology":false,"sense_count":1},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n2693","n2702","n2703","n2704","n2705"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%A8%D9%90%D8%B6%D9%92%D8%B9%D9%8E%D8%A9"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"a few","examples":[{"text":"فِي بِضْعِ سِنِينَ"}]}]},"etymology":null,"ipa":["/bidˤʕ/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n2693","headword_ar":"بَضَعَهُ","root":"bDE","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", (S, Msb,) aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", (Msb,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baDoEN","text_ar":"بَضْعٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, Mgh, Msb, K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He cut it;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, Mgh, Msb, K;) namely, flesh, or flesh-meat: (S, TA:) and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"it"},{"kind":"text","text":"(a sword)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"cut a piece off from it;"},{"kind":"text","text":"namely, a thing: (As, S:) and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he cut it in pieces;"},{"kind":"text","text":"namely, flesh, or flesh-meat: (K, TA:) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bD~Ehu","text_ar":"بضّعهُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"taboDiyEN","text_ar":"تَبْضِيعٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", has the first of these significations: (K: [but only the inf. n. is there mentioned:]) or this latter signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he cut it much,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in several pieces,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in many pieces."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb, TA. *) ―         -b2-"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He slit it;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"cut it lengthwise;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, Mgh, Msb, K;) namely,"},{"kind":"page_break","n":214},{"kind":"text","text":"flesh, or flesh-meat, (Msb,) or a wound, (S, TA,) and a vein, and a hide. (S.) ―         -b3-  [And hence,]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baDaEahaA","text_ar":"بَضَعَهَا"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Sb, Msb, TA,) aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", (Msb,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baDoEN","text_ar":"بَضْعٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"buDoEN","text_ar":"بُضْعٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", like"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$ukorN","text_ar":"شُكْرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$ugolN","text_ar":"شُغْلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kuforN","text_ar":"كُفْرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", for"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fuEolN","text_ar":"فُعْلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is not rare as a measure of inf. ns., (Sb, TA,) or accord. to some it is an inf. n. of this verb, (Msb,) but accord. to others it is a simple subst., (TA,) (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Inivit eam; he lay with her,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"compressed her;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Sb, Msb, K, TA;) as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bADEhA","text_ar":"باضعها","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Msb,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mubaADaEapN","text_ar":"مُبَاضَعَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, Mgh, Msb, K) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"biDaAEN","text_ar":"بِضَاعٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (S, Msb, K:) because in the act which it signifies is a kind of slitting. (Mgh.) You say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"malaka buDoEahaA","text_ar":"مَلَكَ بُضْعَهَا"},{"kind":"text","text":", i. e."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jimaAEahaA","text_ar":"جِمَاعَهَا"},{"kind":"text","text":". (Msb.) And it is said in a prov., ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kamuEal~imapi A^um~ahaA AlbiDaAEa","text_ar":"كَمُعَلِّمَةِ اُمَّهَا البِضَاعَ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)  ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Like her who teaches her mother"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlmujaAmaEap","text_ar":"المُجَامَعَة"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (S.) ―         -b4-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baDoEN","text_ar":"بَضْعٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"also signifies (tropical:)  The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"taking in marriage:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA:) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"buDoEN","text_ar":"بُضْعٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", as an inf. n., (assumed tropical:)  The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"making a contract of marriage."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb.)"}],"source_refs":["S","Msb","Mgh","K","TA","As","Sb"]},{"entry_id":"n2702","headword_ar":"بَضْعَةٌ","root":"bDE","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", (S, Msb, K,) with fet-h, other words of like meaning being with kesr, as"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qiToEapN","text_ar":"قِطْعَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"filo*apN","text_ar":"فِلْذَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fidorapN","text_ar":"فِدْرَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S,) and sometimes with kesr, [↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"biDoEapN","text_ar":"بِضْعَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":",]"},{"kind":"page_break","n":215},{"kind":"text","text":"(K,) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"buDoEapN","text_ar":"بُضْعَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"also is mentioned, (TA,) of which the first is the most chaste, though EshShiháb asserts the second to be more common, (TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A piece,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"lump,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"portion cut off;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA;) particularly"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of flesh,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"flesh-meat,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, Msb, K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in a compact,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"collective, state:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA:) pl. ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baDoEN","text_ar":"بَضْعٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", [or rather this is a coll. gen. n., of which"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baDoEapN","text_ar":"بَضْعَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is the n. un.,] and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"biDaEN","text_ar":"بِضَعٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, Msb, K,) as some say, (S,) but this is disallowed by 'Alee Ibn-Hamzeh, (TA,) [or it may be a correct pl. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"biDoEapN","text_ar":"بِضْعَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"agreeably with analogy,] and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"biDaAEN","text_ar":"بِضَاعٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baDaEaAtN","text_ar":"بَضَعَاتٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Msb, K,) and [quasi-pl. n.]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baDiyEN","text_ar":"بَضِيعٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", which is extr., like"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rahiynN","text_ar":"رَهِينٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kaliybN","text_ar":"كَلِيبٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maEiyzN","text_ar":"مَعِيزٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[&c.]. (TA.) Hence the saying [of Mohammad] in a trad.,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faATimapu baDoEapN min~aY yariybuniY maA raAbahaA wayuw^o*iyniY maA","text_ar":"فَاطِمَةُ بَضْعَةٌ مِنَّى يَرِيبُنِى مَا رَابَهَا وَيُوْذِينِى مَا"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A=*aAhaA","text_ar":"ا=ذَاهَا"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"(tropical:)  Fátimeh is a part of me: [that displeases and disquiets me which has displeased and disquieted her, and that hurts me which has hurt her:"},{"kind":"text","text":"] or, accord. to one relation, he said"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"buDayoEapN","text_ar":"بُضَيْعَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a little part"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (TA.) One says also,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_in~a fulaAnFA","text_ar":"اـِنَّ فُلَانًا"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"la$adiydu AlbaDoEapi HasanuhaA","text_ar":"لَشَدِيدُ البَضْعَةِ حَسَنُهَا"},{"kind":"text","text":"meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Verily such a one is corpulent and fat."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) ―         -b2-  See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baDaEapN","text_ar":"بَضَعَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"."}],"source_refs":["S","Msb","K","TA"]},{"entry_id":"n2703","headword_ar":"بُضْعَةٌ","root":"bDE","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baDoEapN","text_ar":"بَضْعَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"."}],"source_refs":[]},{"entry_id":"n2704","headword_ar":"بِضْعَةٌ","root":"bDE","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baDoEapN","text_ar":"بَضْعَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": and, as a noun of number, see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"biDoEN","text_ar":"بِضْعٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", latter half of the paragraph."}],"source_refs":[]},{"entry_id":"n2705","headword_ar":"بَضَعَةٌ","root":"bDE","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"sound of cutting"},{"kind":"text","text":"of swords: occurring in the saying,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"samiEotu lils~iyaATi xaDaEapF walils~uyuwfi baDaEapF","text_ar":"سَمِعْتُ لِلسِّيَاطِ خَضَعَةً وَلِلسُّيُوفِ بَضَعَةً"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I heard a sound of falling of the whips, and a sound of cutting of the swords:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA:) but in the S and A in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xDE","text_ar":"خضع"},{"kind":"text","text":", and by IB,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xDEp","text_ar":"خضعة"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bDEp","text_ar":"بضعة"},{"kind":"text","text":"are written"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xaDoEapN","text_ar":"خَضْعَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baDoEapN","text_ar":"بَضْعَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"; and IB explains the former as signifying the sounds of swords; and the latter, the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"sounds of whips."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xDE","text_ar":"خضع"},{"kind":"text","text":".) [See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baADiEN","text_ar":"بَاضِعٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":".]"}],"source_refs":["TA"]}]}}